{"id":30427,"date":"2022-10-04T14:54:57","date_gmt":"2022-10-04T14:54:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wappier.com\/?p=30427"},"modified":"2022-10-04T15:31:58","modified_gmt":"2022-10-04T15:31:58","slug":"mobile-game-revenue-statistics","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wappier.com\/mobile-game-revenue-statistics\/","title":{"rendered":"The Big List of Top-Earning Mobile Game Revenue Statistics"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"30427\" class=\"elementor elementor-30427\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-section-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-141ffe1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"141ffe1\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e0362c6\" data-id=\"e0362c6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5351eb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b5351eb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>As much as making your game stand out depends on creativity and artistic vision, ensuring it has healthy financial prospects demands data. Learning lessons from other games that have seen the most success historically, as well as the biggest games of today, is essential to giving your own title the best chance for long-term profitability. With that need in mind, we put together this guide to the most successful mobile games across four leading metrics.<\/p><p><strong>Jump to a section\u2026<\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#_8n7fubmyez06\">What Are the Top-Grossing Mobile Game Genres?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><a href=\"#_iougy6fk5ms4\">Top-Grossing Mobile Game Genres and Their Highest Earners<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#_f6ccdp2wwksu\">What Are the Top-Grossing Mobile Games of All Time?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><a href=\"#_875n33dhp8pp\">Top-grossing mobile games since January 1, 2014<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#_7etiqd6ob0x1\">What Are the Top Mobile Games by Monthly Revenue?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><a href=\"#_yturp02wx66a\">Leading iPhone games by monthly revenue for June 2022<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><a href=\"#_a0k09n3cfr5i\">Leading Android games by monthly revenue for June 2022<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#_ffslrefwz316\">What Are the Top Mobile Games by Downloads?<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><strong><a href=\"#_jc6fqto4v1yl\">Most-downloaded mobile games in the US in 2021<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><a href=\"#_6m3c32pken6w\">Make More With What You Already Have Through Intelligently Optimized IAP Pricing<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bf1ce0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"3bf1ce0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;motion_fx_motion_fx_scrolling&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_effect&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_direction&quot;:&quot;negative&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_speed&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:4.5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;motion_fx_translateY_affectedRange&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;%&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:100}},&quot;motion_fx_devices&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_8n7fubmyez06\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2094047 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2094047\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What Are the Top-Grossing Mobile Game Genres?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3363cdf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3363cdf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Genre is <a href=\"https:\/\/scontent-ort2-2.xx.fbcdn.net\/v\/t39.8562-6\/117296551_345838253479311_5772329102849541721_n.pdf?_nc_cat=106&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=ae5e01&amp;_nc_ohc=gYG7pRcSNkMAX-q4Wnx&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-ort2-2.xx&amp;oh=00_AT-Rr9GIeM1FcKiqSyFTJszpRfqlJAajGVfN7UI7TE1saA&amp;oe=63214B5D\">the most decisive factor<\/a> in what mobile game players choose to play, even moreso than word-of-mouth from friends and family. But even if a player is only interested in, for example, testing their strategic might, the dizzying breadth of mobile games available means there will be fierce competition for <em>which<\/em> strategy game that player decides to spend their time (and disposable income) on.<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.data.ai\/en\/go\/state-of-mobile-2022\/\">Data.ai\u2019s latest State of Mobile report<\/a> breaks down mobile game revenue by genre through 2021, as well as which games took the top spot in each category. While three different subgenres of RPG made the top 10, strategy games only needed one subgenre to claim the top spot overall. Also of interest is the fact that even the most popular category of casino games still fell well short of earning its way into the top three.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c01973 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"3c01973\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_iougy6fk5ms4\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee70016 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ee70016\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3>Top-Grossing Mobile Game Genres and Their Highest Earners<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dc98e8a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dc98e8a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ol><li>Strategy \u2014 4X March-Battle: <strong>$9.7 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Rise of Kingdoms (Lilith Games)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>RPG \u2014 MMORPG: <strong>$8.4 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Lineage M (NCSOFT)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>RPG \u2014 Team Battle: <strong>$8.02 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Fate\/Grand Order (Aniplex)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Casino \u2014 Slots: <strong>$5.57 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Slotomania (Playtika)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Match \u2014 M3-Meta: <strong>$3.92 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Homescapes (Playrix)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Shooting \u2014 Battle Royale: <strong>$3.63 billion<\/strong><ol><li>PUBG Mobile (Tencent Games)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Match \u2014 M3 Saga: <strong>$2.82<\/strong> <strong>billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Candy Crush Saga (King.com)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>RPG \u2014 Puzzle RPG: <strong>$2.25 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Monster Strike (mixi, XFLAG)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Sports \u2014 Simulation Sports: <strong>$2.18 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: Professional Baseball Spirits A (Konami)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><li>Simulation \u2014 Creative Sandbox: <strong>$2.15 billion<\/strong><ol><li>Top earner: ROBLOX (Roblox Corporation)<\/li><\/ol><\/li><\/ol><p>Generating reliable revenue over time isn\u2019t a one-and-done solution for any game, regardless of genre. Setting the right IAP prices is a continuous balancing act that requires attending to numerous factors, from individual user profile to regional economies to fluctuating currencies and everything in between. If you\u2019d like to learn more about how to make sure your IAP is always operating at its full potential, check out our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/url?q=https:\/\/resources.wappier.com\/in-app-purchase-pricing-strategy&amp;sa=D&amp;source=docs&amp;ust=1663177362727415&amp;usg=AOvVaw16fGDwEfL4yHhwxgeOXeyQ\">Complete Guide to In-App Purchase Pricing<\/a>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51986a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"51986a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/resources.wappier.com\/in-app-purchase-pricing-strategy\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1024\" height=\"510\" src=\"https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9-1024x510.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-29930\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9-1024x510.png 1024w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9-300x150.png 300w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9-768x383.png 768w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9-1536x766.png 1536w, https:\/\/wappier.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/image-9.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de88b35 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"de88b35\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_f6ccdp2wwksu\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-230e74d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"230e74d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What Are the Top-Grossing Mobile Game Genres?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8e9912 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b8e9912\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>While mobile games have changed the shape of video gaming as a whole in the last decade, mobile games themselves have also changed quite a bit too. Mobile game publishers looking toward what\u2019s next should consider what has worked so far by taking a close look at the mobile game revenue statistics of top-grossing titles.<\/p><p>Fortunately, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pocketgamer.biz\/feature\/77017\/top-10-highest-grossing-mobile-games-of-all-time\/list\/\">Pocket Gamer partnered with Sensor Tower<\/a> to assemble the following list of the highest-grossing mobile games of all time, providing invaluable insight into the history of the medium. Before we get into the figures, there are two important things to note: Sensor Tower\u2019s data only goes back to January 1, 2014, so any revenue collected by mobile games before then is not counted; and since these figures are cumulative, games that have been out for longer will naturally have an advantage.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de269e0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"de269e0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_875n33dhp8pp\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d7dd55 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8d7dd55\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3>Top-grossing mobile games since January 1, 2014<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4fceb9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f4fceb9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ol><li>Honor of Kings \/ Arena of Valor (Tencent Games): <strong>$12.1 billion<\/strong> grossed since release on November 26, 2015<\/li><li>Monster Strike (mixi, XFLAG): <strong>$9.9 billion<\/strong> grossed since January 1, 2014 (initial release August 8, 2013)<\/li><li>PUBG Mobile (Tencent Games): <strong>$8.4 million<\/strong> grossed since release on March 19, 2018<\/li><li>Clash of Clans (Supercell): <strong>$8.3 billion<\/strong> grossed since January 1, 2014 (initial release August 2, 2012)<\/li><li>Candy Crush Saga (King.com): <strong>$7.5 billion<\/strong> grossed since January 1, 2014 (initial release April 12, 2012)<\/li><li>Puzzle &amp; Dragons (GungHo Online, Nintendo): <strong>$6.2 billion<\/strong> grossed since January 1, 2014 (initial release February 20, 2012)<\/li><li>Fate\/Grand Order (Aniplex): <strong>$6.2 billion<\/strong> grossed since release on July 29, 2015<\/li><li>Pok\u00e9mon GO (Niantic, Inc.): <strong>$6.1 billion<\/strong> grossed since release on July 6, 2016<\/li><li>Fantasy Westward Journey (NetEase Games): <strong>$5.3 billion<\/strong> grossed since release on March 26, 2015<\/li><li>Roblox (Roblox Corporation): <strong>$4.3 billion<\/strong> grossed since January 1, 2014 (initial release September 1, 2006)<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9fabe39 elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"9fabe39\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_7etiqd6ob0x1\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-abb332a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"abb332a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>What Are the Top Mobile Games by Monthly Revenue?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0de67ff elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0de67ff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Just as important as looking at the historical picture of all-time revenue is looking at what mobile games are generating big\u00a0 revenues \u00a0right now. To that end, we\u2019re also featuring these US mobile game revenue figures collected by Statista for the month of June 2022. The results are broken out between <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/691505\/leading-mobile-games-iphone-us-revenue\/\">iPhone<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/690180\/leading-mobile-games-google-play-usa-revenue\/\">Android<\/a>, showing once again that players across the two mobile operating systems have fairly distinct tastes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0525a9b elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"0525a9b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_yturp02wx66a\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df3f855 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"df3f855\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3>Leading iPhone games by monthly revenue for June 2022<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dff7ee8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dff7ee8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ol><li>Candy Crush Saga: <strong>$8.5 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Pok\u00e9mon GO: <strong>$7.5 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Roblox: <strong>$5.8 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Royal Match: <strong>$4.1 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Clash of Clans: <strong>$3.6 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Evony: <strong>$3.1 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Coin Master: <strong>$2.9 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Homescapes: <strong>$2.7 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Diablo Immortal: <strong>$2.7 million<\/strong><\/li><li>Call of Duty: Mobile: <strong>$2.5 million<\/strong><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-976909d elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"976909d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_a0k09n3cfr5i\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e34c27a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e34c27a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t