t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73b42ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"73b42ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Just as essential as breaking out mobile game revenue by genre or any other earnings-centric statistic is how many users have downloaded the app. Simply getting game into people\u2019s hands\u00a0 can be <a href=\"https:\/\/9to5mac.com\/2022\/08\/05\/mobile-games\/\">one of the greatest challenges for mobile game publishers<\/a>, and a download today could lead to a converted customer tomorrow. Therefore, we\u2019d be remiss to end this roundup of mobile games revenue statistics without including the most-downloaded games as well, thanks to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/1285048\/us-top-gaming-apps-by-downloads\/\">Statista\u2019s<\/a> accounting of U.S. 2021 figures.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d1be29e elementor-widget elementor-widget-menu-anchor\" data-id=\"d1be29e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"menu-anchor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"_jc6fqto4v1yl\" class=\"elementor-menu-anchor\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-935161a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"935161a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3>Most-downloaded mobile games in the US in 2021<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fd8d734 elementor-widget elemen